Weil, author of "Eating Well

00:00:38.090 --> 00:00:40.010 align:middle line:90%
for Optimum Health."

00:00:40.010 --> 00:00:44.000 align:middle line:84%
At last, a book about
eating, and eating well,

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.580 align:middle line:90%
for health and pleasure.

00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:49.790 align:middle line:84%
Andrew Weil, author of "Eating
Well for Optimum Health,"

00:00:49.790 --> 00:00:53.120 align:middle line:84%
